H0.text: What is the equivalent rank in the British Army of the German rank Oberst. Brigadier

H1.text: What is the equivalent rank in the British Army of the German rank Oberst. Lieutenant Colonel

H2.text: What is the equivalent rank in the British Army of the German rank Oberst. Major General

H3.text: What is the equivalent rank in the British Army of the German rank Oberst. COLONEL

A4.text: Oberst is a senior field officer rank in several German-speaking and Scandinavian countries, equivalent to Colonel.

A5.text: Oberst in the Bundeswehr is rated OF-5 in NATO, and is grade A16 or B3 in the pay rules of the Federal Ministry of Defence.
